# Lab 03 - IP Addressing Practice

## 🎯 Objective

To configure IPv4 addresses on multiple computers connected through a switch and verify communication using the Ping command.

---

## 🛠 Devices Used

- 1 Cisco 2960 Switch
- 4 PCs

---

## 🌐 IP Configuration

### Admin-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.10

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

---

### HR-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.20

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

---

### Finance-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.30

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

---

### IT-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.40

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

---

## 🧪 Verification

Ping was successfully performed between the computers to verify network connectivity.

---

## 📚 Learning Outcome

After completing this lab, I learned:

- IPv4 Address Configuration
- Device Communication
- Network Connectivity Testing
- Basic LAN Configuration
- Ping Verification

